{"tid":1933477,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎個friend】劇名含侮辱性 《李屍朝鮮》播出兩季後改名","createTime":"2020-03-19T10:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T10:15:50.000Z","uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"547bd2bc853a122c5b2b52a5db76d6c3eadbe4bc","tid":1933477,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/3/1584602270_tT-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F3%2F1584602270_tT-1280w.jpg&h=599d144d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNetflix熱播南韓原創劇集《李屍朝鮮》，本月播出第二季後，引來劇迷熱烈討論，但有南韓網民提出，《李屍朝鮮》的中譯名稱，帶有侮辱性而要求Netflix更改處名。<br />\n<br />\n原來「李氏朝鮮」於韓國人的歷史裡，是日本殖民統治下的蔑稱，而且加入一個「屍」諧音，更讓不少南韓網民感到有問題，因為此劇的韓語及英語片名，是用「王國」或「Kingdom」，Netflix對此亦作出回應：「Netflix 感謝各方對於原創韓劇《李屍朝鮮》中文片名的相關意見與賜教，我們已充分了解並將會盡快做出修改，並盡速再發布通知公告。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/3/1584602272_KQ-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F3%2F1584602272_KQ-1280w.jpg&h=912d88ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E5%8A%87%E5%90%8D%E5%90%AB%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E6%80%A7-%E3%80%8A%E6%9D%8E%E5%B1%8D%E6%9C%9D%E9%AE%AE%E3%80%8B%E6%92%AD%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%A3%E5%BE%8C%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D-212016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F%25E5%258A%2587%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2590%25AB%25E4%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E3%2580%258A%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25B1%258D%25E6%259C%259D%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E3%2580%258B%25E6%2592%25AD%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2590%258D-212016&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFQ7Fv2waV%2FkF2w15sEbuDLw%3D&h=f007679c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E5%8A%87%E5%90%8D%E5%90%AB%E4%B